{
  "id": "698abafdd97de3a810cb0b66",
  "title": "AIで要約した方がマイノリティ意見の取りこぼしリスクが減る",
  "created": 1770699519,
  "updated": 1770819579,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "698abafdd97de3a810cb0b66",
      "text": "AIで要約した方がマイノリティ意見の取りこぼしリスクが減る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699519,
      "updated": 1770699519
    },
    {
      "id": "698abaff00000000006991d6",
      "text": "これ、逆のことを思ってる人が割といる[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699519,
      "updated": 1770699543
    },
    {
      "id": "698abb1600000000006991d8",
      "text": "\tTwitterで説明すると文脈が足りなくてすれ違いになりそうなのでCosenseで一旦書く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699543,
      "updated": 1770699570
    },
    {
      "id": "698abb3300000000006991d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699571,
      "updated": 1770699571
    },
    {
      "id": "698abb3300000000006991da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699571,
      "updated": 1770699571
    },
    {
      "id": "698abb3300000000006991db",
      "text": "N=10000人いて、M=100人の[マイノリティ]の意見があるとする",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770699572,
      "updated": 1770726503
    },
    {
      "id": "698abb4700000000006991dc",
      "text": "データを読む人のリソースが限られていてK=100件しか読めないとする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699591,
      "updated": 1770699627
    },
    {
      "id": "698abb7100000000006991dd",
      "text": "選択肢1: ランダムサンプリングする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699633,
      "updated": 1770699644
    },
    {
      "id": "698abb7b00000000006991de",
      "text": "\t100件の中にマイノリティの意見が入らない確率が37%ある(近似)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699644,
      "updated": 1770819485
    },
    {
      "id": "698c8faf000000000078f0c2",
      "text": "\t\t[gpt.icon]選択肢1 (A): ランダムに `K` 件読む -> `P_miss ≈ exp(-K * M/N) = exp(-1) ≈ 0.368` で、約37%の確率でマイノリティ意見を1件も見ない (厳密計算だと約36.4%)。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770819504,
      "updated": 1770819579
    },
    {
      "id": "698abb9f00000000006991df",
      "text": "選択肢2: AIで要約する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699680,
      "updated": 1770699705
    },
    {
      "id": "698abbb800000000006991e0",
      "text": "\t要約して類似のものを1件にまとめると1%以上の割合を占める意見は確実に上位K=100件に入る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699705,
      "updated": 1770699784
    },
    {
      "id": "698abc0800000000006991e1",
      "text": "\tM=100は1%以上の割合を占めるので取りこぼさない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699784,
      "updated": 1770699799
    },
    {
      "id": "698abc1700000000006991e2",
      "text": "\tQ: 何位に入るのか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699799,
      "updated": 1770796243
    },
    {
      "id": "698c34d30000000000779a1a",
      "text": "\t\t意見クラスタのサイズが[ジップの法則]に従うとしたとき...",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796243,
      "updated": 1770796795
    },
    {
      "id": "698abc1700000000006991e3",
      "text": "\t\t\t[ジップの法則 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%82%B8%E3%83%83%E3%83%97%E3%81%AE%E6%B3%95%E5%89%87]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699799,
      "updated": 1770796288
    },
    {
      "id": "698abb0000000000006991d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770699520,
      "updated": 1770699520
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36720000000000779a1e",
      "text": "[GPT.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796659,
      "updated": 1770796667
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36720000000000779a1f",
      "text": "\tZipf 的な分布だと何が起きるか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796659,
      "updated": 1770796668
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a21",
      "text": " Zipf っぽい世界では、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796671
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a22",
      "text": "  ごく少数の巨大クラスタ (多数派) が全体の大部分を占める",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796671
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a23",
      "text": "  その一方で「小さいクラスタ (マイノリティ)」が大量に存在する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796671
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a24",
      "text": "\tこのときランダムサンプリングは 確率的に「質量の大きいクラスタ」に強く偏るので、ロングテール側は `K` をかなり大きくしないと観測に乗らない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796677
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a27",
      "text": "\tα を変えたときの計算 (`N=10,000`, `M` 固定なし)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796686
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a28",
      "text": "\t\tここでは `n_r = C / r^α` かつ `n_r >= 1` までを実在クラスタとし、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796687
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a29",
      "text": "\t\t`Σ_{r=1..M_eff} n_r = N` を満たすように `C` と `M_eff` を決める。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796690
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a2a",
      "text": "\t\t「1%の順位」は `p_r = n_r / N` が 1% に最も近い rank とする。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796708
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a2b",
      "text": " table:_",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796718
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a2c",
      "text": " \tα\tM_eff\t1位シェア p_1\t1% の順位(付近)\t1%以上の最大順位",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796718
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a2d",
      "text": " \t0.8\t2457\t5.16%\t8位\t7位",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796718
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a2e",
      "text": " \t1.0\t1291\t12.92%\t13位\t12位",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796718
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a2f",
      "text": " \t1.2\t648\t23.69%\t14位\t13位",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796718
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a30",
      "text": " \t1.4\t339\t34.93%\t13位\t12位",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770796718
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36740000000000779a31",
      "text": "\t大体13位くらいになるのか[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796660,
      "updated": 1770819310
    },
    {
      "id": "698c8eef000000000078f0c0",
      "text": "\t\tじゃあ「K=100件しか読めないとする」のところを20にしてもいいのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770819312,
      "updated": 1770819349
    },
    {
      "id": "698c8f3e000000000078f0c1",
      "text": "\t\tK=25のとき確率0.779で見落とす",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770819390,
      "updated": 1770819423
    },
    {
      "id": "698c36730000000000779a20",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796659,
      "updated": 1770796659
    },
    {
      "id": "698c35d60000000000779a1b",
      "text": "もっと雑な説明",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796503,
      "updated": 1770796507
    },
    {
      "id": "698c35db0000000000779a1d",
      "text": "\t要約によって「大勢が似た意見を持っている意見グループ」ほど強く圧縮される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796507,
      "updated": 1770796548
    },
    {
      "id": "698c35db0000000000779a1c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1770796507,
      "updated": 1770796507
    }
  ]
}